high_descs: Move to go face the round black table on the left of the leftmost chair.
Pick up the red credit card that's on the table behind the lamp.
Bring the credit card with you and face the chair that's just to the right of the table you picked it up from.
Put the credit card down on the seat of the chair.
Turn around and face the coffee table so that the remote control is in front of the golden statue when you look at it.
Pick up the credit card from the center of the coffee table.
Bring the credit card back to the same chair that you left the other one on.
Put the credit card down on the seat to the right of the first one.
anns.task_desc: move the credit cards to the chair.

high_descs: Turn around, go across the room, turn left, go across the room and then turn right toward the round table in the corner.
Pick up the credit card on the table.
Turn right and go to the first chair.
Put the credit card on the chair.
Turn around and go to the coffee table.
Pick up the credit card on the coffee table.
Turn to the left and go back to the chair on the left.
Put the credit card on the chair to the right of the other card.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on the chair.

high_descs: Turn right, step forward, turn right, walk to the sofa, turn left and walk to the wall, turn right and walk to the nightstand.
Pick up the credit card on the table behind the lamp.
Turn around, walk forward, turn left, step, forward, then turn left to face the sofa.
Place the credit card on the sofa cushion.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn to the table on the left.
Pick up the credit card in the center of the table.
Turn left and walk forward to the sofa.
Place the credit card on the sofa to the right of the other credit card.
anns.task_desc: Find two credit cards and place on the sofa.
